                  <td class="fallback-font" style="padding: 0; font-weight:normal; font-family: Arial, arial;line-height:22.4px;font-size:14px;color:#363636"><p><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13pt;">Thresholds - Social Work Students&nbsp;</span></strong><br />Thresholds provides services and resources for persons with serious mental illnesses and substance use disorders in Illinois. They believe that everyone deserves the opportunity to live an independent, healthy life and break the cycles of poverty.<br /><br />The Veterans Project within Thresholds is looking for bachelor's and master's level clinicians to fill the position of Community Support Specialist. Knowledge and skills working with the mental health population and/or the veteran population is favorable. Salary level is higher for those who are currently in or served in the Military. Weekly LCSW supervision is provided. Competitive pay, benefits, and generous PTO is offered.<br /><br />Apply <a style="color: #d50032;" title="Thresholds application link" href="https://recruiting.ultipro.com/THR1001THRSH/JobBoard/13bbc74d-d854-4401-ace1-c2cacfa586b0/OpportunityDetail?opportunityId=d53f64ee-e99f-4886-bc00-e7cffd85eaf0" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="color: #d50032; font-weight: bold;">here</span></a>, select careers at <a style="color: #d50032;" title="Thresholds.org link" href="https://www.thresholds.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="color: #d50032; font-weight: bold;">Thresholds.org</span></a>, or contact Veronica Ortiz at <a style="color: #d50032;" title="Email Veronica Ortiz" href="mailto:veronica.ortiz@thresholds.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="color: #d50032; font-weight: bold;">veronica.ortiz@thresholds.org</span></a> or 872-588-5623.<br /></span></p></td>
